Neubot internals
================

This directory contains images and documentation re Neubot internals.

Index
-----

bigpicture.svg
  The relation between objects of the internal classes.

classes.svg
  How the internal classes are linked together.

close.svg
  What happens when the application invokes ``protocol.close()``.

connect.svg
  The steps required to create a new connection (these steps are very
  similar to the ones required to ``accept`` a new connection.)

exception.svg
  What happens when ``connection.readable()`` or ``connection.writable()``
  raise an exception.

readable.svg
  What happens when the connection becomes readable.

writable.svg
  What happens when the application invokes ``protocol.sendmessage()``.
